address2: 6th and 10th Floors Complex Rasuna Epicentrum Jl. H.R. Rasuna Said, Kuningan
longBusinessSummary: PT Bumi Resources Minerals Tbk, through its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration and development of mineral properties in Asia. It operates through three segments: Investments, Holding Company, and Mining and Services. The company explores for lead, zinc, gold, copper, and iron ore. It also invests in shares of stock, as well as engages in funding and financing activities; and offers mining advisory and marketing services. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia.
